General
-------

Source high-lighting:
:source-highlighter: pygments

To get the <1> to nice markers
:icons: font

To get  a blank line
{empty} +

Asciidoctor and deck.js

Put the following after the doc title
:backend: deckjs

* Link ..../github/asciidoctor-deckjs/deck.js to the pwd where ur asciidoc is present.

asciidoctor -T ../github/asciidoctor-backends/haml doc.asciidoc
